						<summary>

						<p>Hero-stone set up near the Barmadēva temple.</p>						

						<p>Vikramāditya VI [A.D. 1126].</p>						

						<p>This inscription is dated in the Chālukya-Vikrama kāla 50, Parābhava, Nija-Chaitra śu 1, Sunday. The date is irregular.</p>						

						<p>It records the death of Gommiseṭṭi of Mūḍevūr in a fight when a <hi rend="italic">Mahāmaṇḍalēśvara</hi> (name not specified) was ruling over Banavāsi-12000. </p>						

						</summary>
