<!--<h4>Panel-I.</h4>-->

<p>
<lb n="1"/>svasti samadhigatapaṁcamahāsabda mahāmaṇḍa
<lb n="2" break="no"/>ḷēsvara banavāsipannirccāsiramanāḷuttami
<lb n="3" break="no"/>re cāḷukhya vikramakālada 50 Ai<unclear>vatta</unclear>ne
</p>

<!--<h4>Panel-II.</h4>-->

<p>
<lb n="4" break="no"/>ya parābhavasaṁvatsa<unclear>ra</unclear> nija caitra suddha 1 Ādivāradaṁdu mū
<lb n="5" break="no"/>ḍevūra gommiseṭṭi <gap reason="lost" quantity="10" unit="character"/> maguḻdu kādi
<lb n="6"/>sattanu maṁgaḷa mahā śrī śrī śrī
</p>

